    "AI-Independent Coders comprised 20.55% of the participants.",
    "The least represented categories were AI-Reliant Code Generator & Refiners (10.27%) and AI-Collaborative Coders (10.96%).",
    "In the second session, the most common interaction profiles were AI-Reliant Code Generator & Refiners (31.51%) and AI-Assisted Code Refiners (29.45%), followed by AI-Reliant Code Generators (21.92%).",
    "The least common categories were AI-Collaborative Coders (11.64%) and AI-Independent Coders (5.48%).",
    "In the third session, nearly half of the students were AI-Collaborative Coders (51.37%)."
